            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "日本首相高市早苗承諾加緊應對通膨並加強國防；日圓短暫跌破153關口",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Sanae Takaichi Photographer: Eugene Hoshiko/AP/Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/8_E4_e1tH1dE0y77BO84CQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/vi/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/3490189dfcacb7f0b6fdabf12c2722c3\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Sanae Takaichi Photographer: Eugene Hoshiko/AP/Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 日本首相高市早苗對國會發表上任後的首次講話，承諾優先解決民眾生活成本問題並將加強國防，承諾推行具有戰略性和負責任的擴張財政政策。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高市尋求在此次講話中表明，她將對選民關切的問題作出迅速反應，同時突出在安全問題上擬採取更強硬立場的打算。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">她表示，「本屆內閣的首要任務是應對通貨膨脹，這是目前困擾日本民眾的一個問題。」她重申，已下令制定一攬子經濟計畫，以減輕家庭成本上漲的負擔，並將在本屆國會上提交一份追加預算來應對這一問題。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-5929bc6a-6741-356d-a27c-d1f27537cacd-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：日本核心通膨率四個月來首次上升 新首相面臨緩解生活成本壓力的挑戰</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日圓表現遜於其他G-10貨幣，兌美元匯率盤中一度下跌0.3%，短暫穿破153關口。日圓本周已下跌約1.5%，是其他G-10貨幣跌幅的兩倍多。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">長期日債周五小幅上揚，高市在講話中沒有提到任何大規模債券發行。新財務大臣片山皋月早些時候暗示，如果現有資源不夠，可能有必要額外發行債券以為經濟計畫融資。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/gizZ1IpI9ezMT97qI27R0A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/vi/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/51bf0b9edca0a12bbe9b18f55eca33ec\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"高市早苗攝影師：Eugene Hoshiko/AP/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/dzeqPkTdfNSWNKaPsVQ4SA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/vi/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/5540b567595c7c10aa984f61c8497b93\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">高市早苗攝影師：Eugene Hoshiko/AP/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高市在講話中還承諾，日本將提前實現到2027財年國防開支占GDP比重達到2%的目標，力爭在3月底前達到這一水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我們需要積極加強國防能力的基礎，」她表示，將通過實施即將出台的額外預算措施來實現2%的支出目標。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高市迫切尋求增加國防開支，正值印太地區局勢緊張，以及外界對川普將如何參與地區事務產生質疑之際。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">鑒於川普堅持要求歐洲國家將國防支出提高到GDP的5%，高市致力於加強日本國防實力的承諾可能會受到歡迎。川普下周將訪問亞洲出席在馬來西亞舉行的東協峰會，以及在韓國舉行的APEC領導人會議；他將在此行中與高市舉行會晤。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高市還在講話中談及對中國相關的安全擔憂，表示將會與中方進行坦誠會談，推進雙邊互利關係。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Japan’s Takaichi Pledges Boost to Inflation Response, Defense</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Yen Underperforms G-10 Peers as Investors Weigh Takaichi Speech</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Yoshiaki Nohara.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E9%A6%96%E7%9B%B8%E9%AB%98%E5%B8%82%E6%97%A9%E8%8B%97%E6%89%BF%E8%AB%BE%E5%8A%A0%E7%B7%8A%E6%87%89%E5%B0%8D%E9%80%9A%E8%86%A8%E4%B8%A6%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%B7%E5%9C%8B%E9%98%B2-%E6%97%A5%E5%9C%93%E7%9F%AD%E6%9A%AB%E8%B7%8C%E7%A0%B4153%E9%97%9C%E5%8F%A3-075751198.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-24 16:30:38",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "中國財政部將在香港發行至多40億美元主權債",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 中國計畫在香港發行至多40億美元的美元計價政府債券，這將有助於在離岸市場打造一條更可靠的殖利率曲線。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">財政部發布公告稱，其將於11月3日發行上述債券。具體發行安排將於發行前另行公佈。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國曾於2024在利雅得發行20億美元主權債。2020年，其在香港發行了60億美元這類債券。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China to Sell Up to $4 Billion Sovereign Bonds in Hong Kong</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-435413fe-47c2-37f3-80be-864dca0e2d3f-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E9%83%A8%E5%B0%87%E5%9C%A8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%8C%E8%87%B3%E5%A4%9A40%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E4%B8%BB%E6%AC%8A%E5%82%B5-074001200.html",
